&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for a flexible and motivated Mammographer to join the small friendly Breast Imaging Team in North Devon.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The breast imaging service operates over 2-3 days,offering symptomatic breast clinics, and booked appointments for symptomatic follow up and family history mammograms. There is also a requirement to work in the General department and participate in the out of hours service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note: we are willing to accept applications from candidates who could work part/ full-time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date 20/11/2020&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
